gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString:
CORINE Land Cover is a pan-European land cover inventory with 44 classes.
Initiated in 1985 (the 1990 reference year) the inventory is available for the 1990, 2000, 2006, 2012 and 2018 reference years including change layers 1990-2000, 2006-2012 and 2012-2018.
CORINE Land Cover is part of the European Union’s Copernicus Land Monitoring Service.
